HEADWORD: Haunted
<hw>Haunt"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Inhabited by, or subject to the
visits of, apparitions; frequented by a ghost.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All houses wherein men have lived and died⟦br⟧
Are <qex>haunted</qex> houses.</q> <rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Haunter</ent>⟦br⟧
